164
00:11:19,303 --> 00:11:22,393
Jam berapa saat Profesor pertama kali menelepon?

165
00:11:22,513 --> 00:11:25,213
Setelah ambulans pergi.

166
00:11:25,333 --> 00:11:29,467
Karena kejadian itu, aku jadi lupa tentang ponselmu.

167
00:11:29,991 --> 00:11:31,693
Begitu.

168
00:11:31,813 --> 00:11:34,373
Mungkin ada sedikit rekaman...

169
00:11:35,053 --> 00:11:37,993
