205
00:13:42,703 --> 00:13:44,551
Aku juga.

206
00:13:44,671 --> 00:13:46,600
Aku juga menolak.

207
00:13:46,720 --> 00:13:48,179
Tunggu...

208
00:13:48,299 --> 00:13:50,680
Tidak apa-apa.

209
00:13:50,800 --> 00:13:53,368
Setelah Pak Renno sadar,

210
00:13:53,488 --> 00:13:57,567
kita akan segera tahu siapa pelakunya.

211
00:14:00,009 --> 00:14:03,445
-Benarkan, Conan? -Mungkin.

212
00:14:03,565 --> 00:14:08,354
Dia bahkan akan memberi tahu cara mereka menuntunnya ke tiang.

213
00:14:08,474 --> 00:14:11,762
